# Mobile and Touch Requirements

> **Superseded** tóm tắt: [`03-src-editing-compact.mdc`](./03-src-editing-compact.mdc). Invoke `@40-mobile-touch-requirements` khi hardening form hiện trường.

- During feature delivery, keep mobile/tablet layouts usable without visual breakage.
- Apply full mobile-first/touch hardening after core logic and data flow are stable.
- Interactive controls (button/card/input) should include:
  - `touch-manipulation`
  - `pointer-events-auto`
  - `-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent`
- Mobile sidebar should use overlay and explicit toggle behavior.
- Keep touch targets easy to tap on mobile screens.
